{"tid":2113476,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【終年30歲】三浦春馬自殺離世 家中發現屍體","createTime":"2020-07-18T07:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T08:09:49.000Z","uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f99ef8b60d65a06b9a67e0839542bb0f3c036c41","tid":2113476,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oBrf-W7Pk2CTA_pGWX8ocwwZA2w=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N3EEOI5UDAW46ZC625EL64HBOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoBrf-W7Pk2CTA_pGWX8ocwwZA2w%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN3EEOI5UDAW46ZC625EL64HBOU.jpg&h=983ff0bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三浦春馬在家中被發現屍體。<br />\nA<br />\nA<br />\nA<br />\n日本男星三浦春馬今日被發現在位於港區的寓所中自殺離世，終年30歲。消息指，三浦春馬是在今日下午1時許被發現死亡，初步估計是上吊自殺，經送院後證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n三浦春馬於1997年出道，憑住《14歲的媽媽》上位，並是真人版電影《進擊的巨人》男主角，當年曾與女主角水原希子來港出席首映禮，前年重臨香港拍攝電影《信用欺詐師：香港浪漫篇》，新片《信用欺詐師：公主篇》本月將於日本開畫。三浦春馬曾與新垣結衣傳出地下情，亦跟「J女郎」三吉彩花拍拖。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"a776b91a37c656fb3fd213d9e770c7dbcbd067ef","tid":2113476,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:05:38.000Z","msg":"Alan"},{"pid":"aceb138419176940631dce7e05a622e53c283491","tid":2113476,"uid":332538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"Bloody Monday既佢真係好靚仔"},{"pid":"cf751ae5562321afd6a0a727a48d1cb44509783d","tid":2113476,"uid":312363,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:16:27.000Z","msg":"24小時求助熱線係想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896285560daef2e5d3